You need to use at least Tomcat version **9** — `HttpFilter` was introduced in *Servlet 4.0*.

[Tomcat 8 is providing][1] *Servlet 3.1*, which does not have that class available.

Another approach is to add dependency `javaee-api` when using version 8.

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;javax&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;javaee-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;8.0&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;


  [1]: http://tomcat.apache.org/whichversion.html

